-- BP Ex-Head of Residues Trading Denies Wrongdoing in Singapore Lawsuit
-- Andrea Tan
-- 2010-08-02T00:44:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/bp-ex-head-of-residues-trading-denies-wrongdoing-in-singapore-lawsuit.html

          
          
             Quek Chin Thean, the former head of
residues trading at BP Plc who is being sued by BP for misusing
confidential information, has denied any wrongdoing in court
papers filed July 29 in Singapore.  
